    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295430/extras/76dec3dd85dd8eb3cdfd66f87a100c2f.poster.avif?t=1771668956\" width=1170 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295430/extras/76dec3dd85dd8eb3cdfd66f87a100c2f.webm?t=1771668956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295430/extras/76dec3dd85dd8eb3cdfd66f87a100c2f.mp4?t=1771668956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Type Ride》是一款通过打字召唤单位的打字型塔防游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角曾因骑着摩托、运用高速打字技巧而被称作“Type Rider”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受托解决墨水生命体蔓延的世界后，她决定再次骑上自己的爱车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295430/extras/dcf44c8e36acf9176e8303f35e96fac3.poster.avif?t=1771668956\" width=1170 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295430/extras/dcf44c8e36acf9176e8303f35e96fac3.webm?t=1771668956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295430/extras/dcf44c8e36acf9176e8303f35e96fac3.mp4?t=1771668956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用拥有属性、职业、特殊技能等多种要素、超过50种个性十足的墨水怪物，构筑只属于你的卡组吧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过成功打字即可“打印”并召唤墨水怪物的系统。面对步步逼近的墨水生命体，我们也用召唤来对抗吧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战略性地运用召唤顺序与各种墨盒，让战斗向有利方向推进吧。</p></li></ul>",
